item.title: My Favorite Songs and the Impact Music has had on My Life
item.description: This was first written in May 2021 but due to a mental block I didn't get it uploaded until September 2021 Music has been a massive part of my life for about as long as I remember. Just now, a friend was asking her friends about their favorite songs. That sent me down a spiral about what my favorite music is. Before, I held the position that it was impossible for me to hold a “favorite song” but now, that’s changed.
